posts.title: Clinic ni Kuya Schedule
posts.content:
• Clinic ni Kuya Daniel (Main)

  • Monday

    General Medicine (Adult), Dental (Extraction only), Optical and Ophthalmology

    4:30AM – 8:30AM


  • Tuesday

    General Medicine (adult), Physical Therapy, Ob/gyn, Thyroid screening (Every 1st wk of the month only)

    4:30AM – 8:30AM


  • Wednesday

    General Medicine (Adult), Dental (extraction only), Optical and Ophthalmology, Prostate Consultation (Every last week of the month)

    4:30AM – 8:30AM


  • Thursday

    General Medicine (adult), Dental (Extraction only), Derma (Every 2nd and 3rd week of the month)

    4:30AM – 8:30AM


  • Friday

    General Medicine (Pedia), Dental Pedia (Extraction only)

    4:30AM – 8:30AM
